  <main>
    <section id="services" class="services">
      <%- include('../partials/services.ejs') -%>
    </section>
    <section id="about" class="about">
      <div class="about-section">
        <div class="about-details">
          <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
          <p>Having been in the industry for over 12 years we have a proven track record in repairing mechanical, electrical and hydraulic systems. We have a fully equipped workshop with high precision tools to aid us with repairs and fault diagnosis.</p>
          <p>We have a proven track record within the motoring industry and have received accreditation from multiple trade bodies including the <a href="https://www.rmif.co.uk/en/about-the-rmi" title="Information about the RMI" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">RMI</a> and <a href="https://www.theimi.org.uk/agenda/about-institute-motor-industry-imi" title="Information about the IMI" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">IMI</a>.</p>
          <p>We have also received multiple awards for our work on the trusted <a href="">whocanfixmycar.com</a> website, including their coveted <strong>National Top Performer</strong> and <strong>Gold Customer Service</strong> badges.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-imgs">
          <a href="https://www.whocanfixmycar.com/networks/brembo" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" title="">
            <img src="../../assets/img/brembo-logo.jpg" alt="" height="100">
